RMSDocumentation.Node:
> set_scaling_to_player_number
Scales number_of_groups to the map size. Unscaled value refers to a 100x100 map (see: Map Sizes for the scaling table)
If no grouping is present, scaling applies to number_of_objects instead. <OBJECTS_GENERATION> create_object GOLD { number_of_objects 10 number_of_groups 3 set_scaling_to_map_size set_tight_grouping }
